                "invention-title": [
                    "Photothermal vaporization catalysis and purification integrated hydrogen production reactor",
                    "一种光热汽化催化及提纯一体式制氢反应器"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a photo-thermal vaporization catalysis and purification integrated hydrogen production reactor which comprises a reactor body, the reactor body is provided with a vaporization area, a reaction area and a heat exchange area, the vaporization area is communicated with the reaction area, the vaporization area is located in the heat exchange area, the heat exchange area is connected with the reaction area, reactants enter the reaction area after being heated after entering the vaporization area, and the reaction area is communicated with the reaction area; and the mixed gas flows back into the heat exchange area and exchanges heat with the vaporization area, and then the mixed gas is discharged. External liquid-phase reactants are conveyed into the vaporization area, heat exchange is achieved between the liquid-phase reactants and the heat exchange area, and the liquid-phase reactants are converted into gas-phase reactants; the gas-phase reactant enters the reaction zone to be in contact with a porous catalyst for hydrogen production reaction, and hydrogen-rich synthesis gas is generated; the hydrogen-rich synthesis gas flows back into the heat exchange area through the communication position of the heat exchange area and the reaction area and exchanges heat with a liquid-phase reactant in the vaporization area, waste heat recovery is achieved, and the energy utilization rate is increased."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供了一种光热汽化催化及提纯一体式制氢反应器，包括：反应器本体，设有汽化区、反应区和换热区，汽化区与反应区连通，汽化区位于换热区内，且换热区连接反应区，反应物进入汽化区内被加热后进入反应区内，经催化反应形成混合气体，混合气体回流至换热区内与汽化区换热后排出。将外界的液相反应物输送至汽化区内，液相反应物与换热区实现热交换，转化为气相反应物；气相反应物进入反应区内与多孔催化剂接触发生制氢反应，产生富氢合成气；富氢合成气通过换热区和反应区的连通处回流至换热区内，与汽化区内的液相反应物进行热交换，实现余热回收，提高能量的利用率。"
                }
            ]
